Additional information:

This project provides an efficient, modern driver for 3.5" Raspberry Pi 
displays with ILI9486L controller and XPT2046 touch controller, designed 
to replace aging LCD-show drivers with better performance and Pi 5 compatibility.

The source code is available at: https://github.com/efficient-rpi-display/

Contact: efficient-rpi-display@example.com 